::Iron Raptor/Prowl/Firearm/Cledar/Rixer/Forrior/Blyer::

"The training rooms use holograms. They're fairly advanced, as you'll 
see,"  she says, accessing Prowl's mind and going by what he was 
seeing for the reply to Stronghold's question.

The training room doors open and Iron Raptor enters, smiling when she 
sees Prowl, Firearm, Cledar, Rixer, Forrior, and Blyer turn to her 
and snap to attention.

"Sorry for the delay, Maximals," she says, "I had to talk to these 
bots for a while."

She turns and motions to the new Maximals. "They'll be training with 
us as fellow Maximals."
